WEBVTT

00:00:10.025 --> 00:00:11.111
Oh the humanity!

00:00:13.730 --> 00:00:15.651
Ah... humanity...

00:00:16.210 --> 00:00:19.162
It’s a trainwreck,
but I can’t look away.

00:00:20.206 --> 00:00:23.576
It’s 1843, and a debate is raging 
among physicians

00:00:23.576 --> 00:00:28.089
about one of the most common 
killers of women: childbed fever.

00:00:28.089 --> 00:00:31.569
Childbed fever strikes 
within days of giving birth,